HEADWORD: Subpedunculate
<hw>Sub`pe*dun"cu*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot. &
Zool.)</fld> <def>Supported on, or growing from, a very short stem;
having a short peduncle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

